1
00:00:03,500 --> 00:00:05,040
If AI is going to
revolutionize healthcare...

2
00:00:05,300 --> 00:00:05,960
...who does it for them?

3
00:00:06,360 --> 00:00:07,820
Because they can barely
keep the lights on.

4
00:00:07,820 --> 00:00:09,680
So let's do it for them, right?

5
00:00:10,380 --> 00:00:12,780
What if we provided healthcare AI
as a service?

6
00:00:12,780 --> 00:00:15,140
We find all of those cancers.
We bring them in.

7
00:00:15,440 --> 00:00:17,060
All of your A1Cs greater than nine...

8
00:00:17,060 --> 00:00:19,060
...who haven't followed up
with their primary care doctor...

9
00:00:19,060 --> 00:00:21,260
...in a year, two years -
bring them back in.

10
00:00:21,260 --> 00:00:22,860
All of that health data exists...

11
00:00:22,860 --> 00:00:24,360
...on your health
information exchange.

12
00:00:24,820 --> 00:00:26,620
What if we build
an intelligence layer...

13
00:00:26,620 --> 00:00:28,000
...that sat over the top of that...

14
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:30,240
...constantly crawling
through that data...

15
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:33,120
...looking for signals,
looking for ways to make you better?
